All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
ApplicationError
ApplicationError represents an error response in the application.
AuthController
AuthController handles authentication and user registration requests.
AuthService
AuthService handles authentication and user registration logic in the application.
CloudStorageController
CloudStorageController handles file upload and download requests to the cloud storage.
CloudStorageService
CloudStorageService provides functionalities for uploading and downloading files in the cloud storage.
CustomUserDetailsService
CustomUserDetailsService implements the UserDetailsService interface to provide custom user authentication details for Spring Security.
DataInitializer
DataInitializer is a component that initializes the application data on startup.
JwtRequest
JwtRequest represents a request containing the user's authentication credentials.
JwtRequestFilter
JwtRequestFilter is responsible for filtering each incoming request to check if it contains a valid JWT token.
JwtResponce
JwtResponse represents the response containing the JWT token returned after successful authentication.
JwtTokenUtils
JwtTokenUtils is a utility class for handling JWT (JSON Web Token) operations.
MainController
MainController handles navigation for the main pages of the application.
PracticeProjectApplication
PracticeProjectApplication is the main entry point of the Spring Boot application.
RegistrationUserDto
RegistrationUserDto is a Data Transfer Object (DTO) that contains the user's registration information including username, email, password, and a confirmation of the password.
Role
Role represents an entity that defines a user role in the application.
RoleRepository
RoleRepository is a Spring Data repository interface for accessing role entities in the database.
RoleService
RoleService provides functionalities for managing user roles in the application.
User
User represents an entity that defines a user in the application.
UserDto
UserDto is a Data Transfer Object (DTO) that represents a user in the application.
UserRepository
UserRepository is a Spring Data repository interface for accessing user entities in the database.
WebResourceHandlersConfiguration
WebResourceHandlersConfiguration configures resource handlers for serving static resources.
WebSecurityConfig
WebSecurityConfig configures the security for the application using Spring Security.
